{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2>When Hammlet's wife Prascilla goes missing, Reynard immediately grabs his high-tech gauntlet and goes on an adventure. In order to rescue Prascilla from becoming &quot;Goulash&quot; and his home island Foen from an invasion, he has to defeat many vicious creatures and villains.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2>Reynard is a mixture of procedurally generated action RPG and a Tower Defense genre with roguelike elements. It has been influenced by classics such as The Legend of Zelda and an indie classic - The Binding of Isaac. <br><br>It contains features such as:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Countless proceduraly generated dungeons, TD maps and runes!<br></li><li>More than 200 different items!<br></li><li>Fast paced action against challenging enemies and bosses!<br></li><li>Progression through perk and blueprint system!<br></li><li>Simple yet cool crafting system!<br></li><li>Achievements and daily runs!<br></li><li>Cute player skins!<br></li><li>Lovely story and companions!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Blacksmith","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/970140/0d55cf970a150660d9a3c181d4a0db7ea1755899.jpg"},{"name":"Saviour","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/970140/0453e65ef51a0085f3b527d4f87328ca44f954cc.jpg"},{"name":"I'm gonna be rich!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/970140/4ae756402c9e8f43d325c3c27e1263bd39a08451.jpg"},{"name":"Pot hater","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/970140/acc7b5acf67dfda5caaea853643f29b3c25bbc7f.jpg"},{"name":"Prascilla I'm coming!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/970140/ac93bc7cbc8e17e295cb7fc91c9567abd7ae1d33.jpg"},{"name":"They fall like bricks!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/970140/bf9ec6b3bfaabba2ec18a561a43